---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <section class="hero-box">
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <div class="hero-label">Archive // Collection 2025</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="story-container">
      
      <div class="story-header">
        <span class="blueprint-id">Ref. No. 1974-JVS</span>
        <h2 class="story-title">From Architecture to the Forge</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="story-body">
        <p>
          For the beginning of my adult life I was determined and excited to become an architect and interior designer. While going to college and pursuing this goal, I began taking silver smithing classes as a part of my art requirement.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          I finished college and started my designing career but discovered I was spending a lot of time making things for myself and gifts for others. After quite a few years of trying to live two lives, I determined that the small intricate fascinating world of silver and gold smithing was my stronger passion.
        </p>

        <p>
          I began training in earnest both with professional schooling and master goldsmiths. I've been doing it now for over 20 years and I still love it. There are always new challenges to tackle, wonderful people to meet, problems to solve, and itsy bitsy details to work out.
        </p>

        <p class="cta-text">
          If you have any questions from what you see here, or if you'd like to order something special for yourself or a loved one, please feel free to <a href="/contact">contact me</a>. You can also visit my <a href="https://etsy.com" target="_blank">Etsy Store</a> to find things to tickle your fancy, or follow the workshop's progress on <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank">Instagram</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="signature-block">
          <p>Keep on smiling,</p>
          <p class="name">Jen Van Schmus</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mechanical-footer">
        <div class="gear-dot"></div>
        <div class="long-line"></div>
        <div class="gear-dot"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Reservation */
  .hero-box {
    width: 100%;
    height: 800px;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    background-image: url('/site-assets/hero-main.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .hero-label {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    right: 40px;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    color: #999;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Story Section */
  .story-section {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: #fff;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .story-container {
    max-width: 700px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }

  .story-header {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    border-left: 1px solid #eee;
    padding-left: 30px;
  }

  .blueprint-id {
    display: block;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #ccc;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .story-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .story-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 30px;
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .story-body p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .cta-text {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 30px;
    background: #fafafa;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 1rem !important;
  }

  .cta-text a {
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .cta-text a:hover {
    color: #a18a4d;
  }

  .signature-block {
    margin-top: 40px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .signature-block .name {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 5px;
    color: #111;
  }

  /* Mechanical Footer Decoration */
  .mechanical-footer {
    margin-top: 100px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .long-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: #eee; }
  .gear-dot { 
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border: 1px solid #000; border-radius: 50%; 
    position: relative;
  }
  .gear-dot::after {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 2px; background: #000; border-radius: 50%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-box { height: 500px; }
    .story-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
  }
</style>
